1
00:00:11,760 --> 00:00:13,960
I heard the General likes night riding.

2
00:00:14,060 --> 00:00:15,790
I came especially to serve you.

3
00:00:17,260 --> 00:00:19,100
Our General hates night riding the most.

4
00:00:19,100 --> 00:00:20,330
Everyone in the northwest knows it.

5
00:00:20,330 --> 00:00:23,100
The General gets irritable and bloodthirsty when riding at night.

6
00:00:23,100 --> 00:00:26,360
Even enemy sneak attacks wouldn't dare to happen at night.

7
00:01:05,500 --> 00:01:06,930
Since you don't like it,

8
00:01:06,930 --> 00:01:08,500
I'll take my leave.

9
00:01:11,760 --> 00:01:12,600
Lu Zhong,

10
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,130
prepare a horse.

11
00:01:29,800 --> 00:01:31,530
Why wouldn't I like it?

12
00:01:32,530 --> 00:01:34,990
Isn't this the kind of night riding you want?

13
00:01:35,530 --> 00:01:37,060
General, can you slow down?

14
00:01:37,259 --> 00:01:38,700
It's too bumpy.

15
00:01:44,900 --> 00:01:45,700
Shen Lvyi,

16
00:01:46,229 --> 00:01:48,560
bringing up the past to evoke my memories,

17
00:01:48,759 --> 00:01:49,729
didn't you think

18
00:01:50,360 --> 00:01:53,490
I would also remember your deception and manipulation?

19
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:57,600
You can deceive and manipulate me back.

20
00:01:57,860 --> 00:01:59,590
I'll have no complaints at all.

21
00:02:03,230 --> 00:02:04,400
To seduce me,

22
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:05,930
you actually went this far.

23
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:11,330
You are truly dutiful and lowly.

24
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:13,500
The Shen family has been wronged.

25
00:02:13,500 --> 00:02:14,960
The righteousness of the country

26
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:15,830
and the prosperity of the family

27
00:02:15,830 --> 00:02:17,100
all rely on me.

28
00:02:17,900 --> 00:02:20,430
As for personal feelings,

29
00:02:20,700 --> 00:02:22,930
they are of the least importance to me right now.

30
00:02:22,930 --> 00:02:23,730
Shen Lvyi.

31
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:26,700
Since you tried so hard to seduce me,

32
00:02:27,160 --> 00:02:28,420
I will grant your wish.

33
00:02:29,260 --> 00:02:32,160
You will stay by my side for the rest of your life,

34
00:02:32,600 --> 00:02:34,660
enduring my anger and revenge.

35
00:02:38,760 --> 00:02:41,060
You did a great job in these three days of trial marriage, miss.

36
00:02:41,060 --> 00:02:42,730
This matter is finally over.

37
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:48,690
Some things are probably not over.

38
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:51,600
This game has just begun.

39
00:02:51,860 --> 00:02:54,060
Momo, let's go back and report.

40
00:02:54,060 --> 00:02:56,400
Madam and the Second Miss will definitely reward us.

41
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:59,030
Maybe we'll even get a raise.

42
00:03:00,460 --> 00:03:01,730
Not necessarily.

43
00:03:13,730 --> 00:03:16,329
It really is the Eldest Miss of the Shen family.

44
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:17,200
I didn't expect

45
00:03:17,200 --> 00:03:19,600
she would end up as a trial marriage maid for the Wei family.

46
00:03:19,600 --> 00:03:21,230
She was so glorious before.

47
00:03:21,230 --> 00:03:22,600
The number one noble lady in the capital.

48
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:25,100
Now she's just a tool for people's amusement.

49
00:03:25,100 --> 00:03:27,360
She really lost the face of noble families.

50
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:28,160
Lvyi,

51
00:03:28,700 --> 00:03:30,100
you've worked hard these three days.

52
00:03:30,100 --> 00:03:31,230
You are merciful, Second Miss.

53
00:03:31,230 --> 00:03:33,160
I am willing to share your burdens.

54
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:33,900
Humph.

55
00:03:34,300 --> 00:03:35,100
Indeed.

56
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:36,460
If I wasn't kindhearted

57
00:03:36,460 --> 00:03:38,600
and bought the contracts of all the women in your family,

58
00:03:38,600 --> 00:03:40,860
you would probably have been sold to a brothel by now.

59
00:03:40,860 --> 00:03:42,720
How could you be so relaxed today?

60
00:03:42,829 --> 00:03:43,460
Yes.

61
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:44,930
Thank you, Second Miss.

62
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:45,800
Shen Lvyi,

63
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,260
even at this point,

64
00:03:47,260 --> 00:03:49,000
you still look so arrogant.

65
00:03:49,160 --> 00:03:51,400
I must give you a huge embarrassment.

66
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:53,329
There are no outsiders here.

67
00:03:53,329 --> 00:03:54,360
Tell us,

68
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:56,730
how did you serve the Great General of Weibei?

69
00:03:56,730 --> 00:03:59,060
I heard he is decisive on the battlefield.

70
00:03:59,130 --> 00:04:01,530
He must be very brave in bed too.

71
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:03,800
Everyone is very curious about him.

72
00:04:07,300 --> 00:04:09,030
As you wish, Second Miss.

73
00:04:17,500 --> 00:04:19,160
The General is back from the court.

74
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:21,300
His Majesty rewarded me with two carriages of treasures today.

75
00:04:21,300 --> 00:04:23,360
Take the brothers to divide the gold, silver, and treasures.

76
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:24,700
Don't touch the jewelry and hairpins.

77
00:04:24,700 --> 00:04:26,500
Send them all to the Eldest Miss.

78
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:30,960
General, the Eldest Miss of the Shen family has gone back.

79
00:04:32,700 --> 00:04:33,500
Gone back?

80
00:04:34,260 --> 00:04:35,590
Where did she return to?

81
00:04:35,630 --> 00:04:37,730
Grand... The Grand Tutor's Mansion.

82
00:04:39,430 --> 00:04:41,030
You just let her go like that?

83
00:04:41,100 --> 00:04:43,460
That Wei woman has a sweet face but a cruel heart.

84
00:04:43,460 --> 00:04:45,530
She's in for trouble going back.

85
00:04:45,700 --> 00:04:47,030
I tried to persuade her,

86
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:48,500
but she wouldn't listen.

87
00:04:48,500 --> 00:04:52,030
Eldest Miss Shen said she hopes you won't worry about her anymore,

88
00:04:52,030 --> 00:04:53,630
and stop being angry for her.

89
00:04:53,900 --> 00:04:56,130
From now on, you part ways

90
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:58,200
and find your own happiness.

91
00:05:03,660 --> 00:05:05,230
Who the hell wants to part ways with you

92
00:05:05,230 --> 00:05:06,760
and find our own happiness?

93
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:07,630
Shen Luyi!

94
00:05:08,200 --> 00:05:10,360
I will never let you go in this life!

95
00:05:17,960 --> 00:05:19,100
The General is here.

96
00:05:19,100 --> 00:05:20,700
My master has just returned from the court.

97
00:05:20,700 --> 00:05:21,860
General, please follow me to the front courtyard.

98
00:05:21,860 --> 00:05:22,860
Get out of the way!

99
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:35,130
General Weibei has extraordinary strength,

100
00:05:35,130 --> 00:05:36,830
especially a straight and strong waist.

101
00:05:36,830 --> 00:05:39,090
It's all from years of horseback riding.

102
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:41,030
The ancients said that horses are

103
00:05:41,030 --> 00:05:42,030
the foundation of the military

104
00:05:42,030 --> 00:05:43,730
and of great use to the country.

105
00:05:43,730 --> 00:05:45,500
Riding not only strengthens the body,

106
00:05:45,500 --> 00:05:46,800
but also hones the will.

107
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:49,000
The General's physique and spirit today

108
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:51,330
are inseparable from his years of riding and archery.

109
00:05:51,330 --> 00:05:52,460
You have good taste.

110
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:54,030
You know how good I am.

111
00:05:55,400 --> 00:05:57,000
In fact, if women learn to ride and shoot,

112
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,530
they can also protect and strengthen themselves.

113
00:05:58,530 --> 00:05:59,730
It can also broaden their minds.

114
00:05:59,730 --> 00:06:00,830
When they marry in the future,

115
00:06:00,830 --> 00:06:02,600
they will have common topics with their husbands.

116
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:03,460
Why not do it?

117
00:06:03,460 --> 00:06:04,000
Indeed.

118
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:06,200
I used to think riding and archery were vulgar.

119
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:07,130
Hearing you say this,

120
00:06:07,130 --> 00:06:08,160
makes me want to learn it tomorrow.

121
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:09,260
I want to learn too.

122
00:06:11,130 --> 00:06:12,860
You used to be a lady of a noble family,

123
00:06:12,860 --> 00:06:15,860
yet now you openly discuss a man's waist and strength.

124
00:06:15,960 --> 00:06:17,130
How depraved

125
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:18,330
and shameless.

126
00:06:18,900 --> 00:06:20,100
It was you, Second Miss,

127
00:06:20,100 --> 00:06:21,200
who asked me to publicly speak out

128
00:06:21,200 --> 00:06:23,260
the details of my intimacy with General Weibei

129
00:06:23,260 --> 00:06:24,700
to satisfy everyone's curiosity.

130
00:06:24,700 --> 00:06:26,630
I was merely answering truthfully.

131
00:06:26,630 --> 00:06:28,230
How is that shameless?

132
00:06:28,500 --> 00:06:29,160
Exactly.

133
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:30,360
Going back on your words like this

134
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:31,600
lacks the demeanor of a noble lady.

135
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:33,100
How dare you talk back, you lowly slave!

136
00:06:33,100 --> 00:06:34,860
Someone, slap her face!

137
00:06:36,300 --> 00:06:37,800
In everything I say and do,

138
00:06:37,930 --> 00:06:39,930
I follow the Second Miss's orders.

139
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:41,460
How is it talking back?

140
00:06:41,760 --> 00:06:43,760
Please be reasonable, Second Miss.

141
00:06:44,430 --> 00:06:47,030
You little wench, after sleeping with General Weibei for three days,

142
00:06:47,030 --> 00:06:48,800
you dare to act wild in my Wei family.

143
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:50,300
A deflowered lowly slave.

144
00:06:50,530 --> 00:06:51,930
Marrying you off to the stable boy

145
00:06:51,930 --> 00:06:53,230
is already flattering you.

146
00:06:53,230 --> 00:06:53,960
Guards!

147
00:06:54,230 --> 00:06:56,360
Go to the stables and fetch Lai Mazi.

148
00:06:56,930 --> 00:06:59,530
They shall get married today.

149
00:07:07,330 --> 00:07:08,130
Who are you?

150
00:07:08,130 --> 00:07:09,830
How dare you act wild in the Grand Tutor's Mansion?

151
00:07:09,830 --> 00:07:11,100
General Weibei,

152
00:07:11,530 --> 00:07:12,860
Lu Jingxing.

153
00:07:14,630 --> 00:07:16,030
General Weibei?

154
00:07:16,660 --> 00:07:18,330
Indeed, he has a straight, strong waist,

155
00:07:18,330 --> 00:07:19,460
and a heroic spirit.

156
00:07:19,630 --> 00:07:21,230
Rumor says General Weibei is a god of killing,

157
00:07:21,230 --> 00:07:23,490
but I didn't expect him to be so handsome.

158
00:07:23,830 --> 00:07:24,600
General.

159
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:25,730
Your visit, General,

160
00:07:25,730 --> 00:07:26,660
truly brings honor to my humble home.

161
00:07:26,660 --> 00:07:27,430
Enough.

162
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:29,230
Save the polite bullshit.

163
00:07:29,300 --> 00:07:30,900
I'm not in the mood to listen.

164
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:33,159
I'm here to pick up my person.

165
00:07:35,659 --> 00:07:37,230
She is a servant of the Wei family.

166
00:07:37,230 --> 00:07:38,630
You cannot take her away.

167
00:07:38,659 --> 00:07:39,560
That's right.

168
00:07:40,200 --> 00:07:43,200
I just betrothed her to a stableboy in the mansion.

169
00:07:43,230 --> 00:07:45,030
You are a step too late, General.

170
00:07:47,300 --> 00:07:49,200
Let's talk this out, General.

171
00:07:49,300 --> 00:07:51,000
We are both His Majesty's right-hand men.

172
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:53,659
Why hurt our relationship over a lowly servant?

173
00:07:53,700 --> 00:07:55,800
I saved His Majesty's life on the battlefield in the northwest.

174
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:57,500
His Majesty personally promised

175
00:07:57,500 --> 00:07:58,400
that within the Great Sheng,

176
00:07:58,400 --> 00:08:00,130
whatever I, Lu Jingxing, want,

177
00:08:00,300 --> 00:08:01,800
he will grant me.

178
00:08:01,960 --> 00:08:03,960
Shen Luyi is my person.

179
00:08:04,400 --> 00:08:05,200
If you don't hand her over,

180
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:06,430
I will tear down this Grand Tutor's mansion

181
00:08:06,430 --> 00:08:07,400
and burn it to the ground.

182
00:08:07,400 --> 00:08:08,800
Let's see who can stop me.

183
00:08:08,900 --> 00:08:09,700
Lu Jingxing.

184
00:08:09,900 --> 00:08:11,030
You are too arrogant.

185
00:08:11,030 --> 00:08:12,300
I am the Grand Tutor of the current dynasty

186
00:08:12,300 --> 00:08:13,900
and your future father-in-law.

187
00:08:13,900 --> 00:08:14,960
Who acknowledged that?

188
00:08:14,960 --> 00:08:16,200
Where is the Lu Army?

189
00:08:17,260 --> 00:08:20,200
Here!

190
00:08:23,500 --> 00:08:25,800
Give her back to me.

191
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:27,200
Give her up.

192
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:28,100
Please.

193
00:08:30,830 --> 00:08:32,830
I do not wish to go with you, General.

194
00:08:35,330 --> 00:08:37,799
What did you say, Shen Luyi?

195
00:08:38,059 --> 00:08:41,130
The Wei family took in all the women of my family in our time of need.

196
00:08:41,130 --> 00:08:42,299
They have done me a great favor.

197
00:08:42,299 --> 00:08:43,429
I am unwilling to betray my master

198
00:08:43,429 --> 00:08:44,600
and climb the social ladder with you, General.

199
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:45,460
Something's wrong.

200
00:08:45,460 --> 00:08:49,030
There must be something she wants from the Wei family that she hasn't gotten yet.
